{"tid":1535347,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"以後叫黑警  ----  扑 頭 黨","createTime":"2019-09-03T10:25:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T07:13:27.000Z","uid":83265,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"79cb48c37cd95e5447e0d5cd8df8901db849a913","tid":1535347,"uid":83265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:25:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">有返咁上下年紀既人，特別係藍絲，都應該聽過扑頭黨<br />\n當年扑頭黨係被認為最兇殘的罪案</span><br />\n<br />\n【回歸20年‧扑頭黨】逾10死者沉冤未雪<br />\n<br />\n回歸初期肆虐本港的扑頭劫案，是由內地傳入香港最兇殘的搵快錢罪案，賊人以木棍、磚頭從後扑頭偷襲，趁受害人倒地昏迷搶劫，有時僅劫得一千幾百，但有受害人不幸傷重死亡。至今仍有逾10宗扑頭案未破。其實隨着港府將扑頭案量刑起點增至8年，同類案件一度下降，但2003年沙士疫症重創本港經濟，失業率更升至8.7%歷史高位，往後兩年扑頭案回升，最後在警方打擊下才有減少。<br />\n<br />\n手段冷血兇殘的扑頭劫案有指源於廣州，回歸後來港犯案的最初是偷渡客或持雙程證內地人，其後有本地罪犯模仿犯案，警方當時分析部分扑頭賊偷渡來港潛伏地盤做黑工並伺機犯案。<br />\n<br />\n1999年是扑頭案高峰期，一年內發生154宗扑頭劫案奪去3命，警方重手打擊於各警區設專隊緝捕。2000年，高等法院發出指引，要求所有扑頭劫案交高院審理並把量刑起點定位8年，嚴刑下扑頭案一度下降。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">咁我就依家問下，黑警同扑頭黨有咩分別?? </span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">有，黑警係為興趣 !!! 更為兇殘 </span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">叫黑警做 扑 頭 黨 ，一定能夠令藍絲有所共鳴 </span>  <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed08454f5cfadff1221c0d1e9d87948fe22cab9b","tid":1535347,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:25:39.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"754dcbd404272f2b48226b63291176b61d1f1506","tid":1535347,"uid":83265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:26:08.000Z","msg":"扑頭黨"},{"pid":"6866b19de9963a079748bcb7ab7f861f8131149e","tid":1535347,"uid":83265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:26:18.000Z","msg":"扑頭黨"},{"pid":"1ac67365ce7711eae2b7761b4787eea5c3fcb047","tid":1535347,"uid":290815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:26:30.000Z","msg":"其實要突破困局，依家只有「__」依個選項！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1534823\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1534823</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6c5a929aecbcb4f03b7152d5a294805510318ac4","tid":1535347,"uid":83265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:26:33.000Z","msg":"扑頭黨"},{"pid":"a78ff6c5d15d9113abffd51768c82a9d827046fb","tid":1535347,"uid":255094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:26:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c7fd39eacbc30cf9e681e97d3b1f8a331fc6e41b","tid":1535347,"uid":46674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:27:17.000Z","msg":"扑頭黨"},{"pid":"ec9ffe91d44253015b228c05add2ee0fc66605cd","tid":1535347,"uid":83265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:28:19.000Z","msg":"扑頭黨"},{"pid":"3f85ab62bd29ee182c35a3ffd8a744f6f32581d7","tid":1535347,"uid":83265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T10:30:14.000Z","msg":"佢地已經對